bug.short_desc: Unknown command 'qxClick' when running silenium server

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1278 contents of attachment are stated in report description
When I tried to implement the "Automated UI testing" (4.7.9 Tutorial Part 4.4.1) example I ran into the following issue:
The silenium server posts the following error (command 'generate.py simulation-run):
09:51:16.105 INFO - Got result: ERROR: Unknown command: 'qxClick' on session 33cbedb040a64d4 daad28832211c6db3
The attachment contains
1. The console output of the server 2. The log output of the server, 3. The console output of the command 'generate.py simulation-run' 4. The contents of the extension file user-extensions.js 5. The config.json file 6. The console output of the http server
Really looking forward to your answers.
regards, Lars
